title: Organic Oasis
typeOfFood: Ovo, American, Macrobiotic, Organic, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Meat offered is poultry, otherwise veg. Live music most days. The owner offers nutritional counseling. There is also a small supplements and natural food area and an organic co-op where members purchase dry goods & fresh local produce. Note: The "vegan" meatballs may note be vegan - please check and confirm for HappyCow, thanks.
